    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于”狙击枪”套装</h2><br>另外一个万圣节武器系列等你来！这种武器一定让你的敌人理解到你是一种厉害的战士。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/f6433b15b29cf6642ba5a862a51c5b00.poster.avif?t=1685625982\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/f6433b15b29cf6642ba5a862a51c5b00.webm?t=1685625982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/f6433b15b29cf6642ba5a862a51c5b00.mp4?t=1685625982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这些枪的梦幻般的外观一定会给对手留下深刻印象并让您高兴。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/4679925d72a52a749c0d5d6200ff704d.poster.avif?t=1685625982\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/4679925d72a52a749c0d5d6200ff704d.webm?t=1685625982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/4679925d72a52a749c0d5d6200ff704d.mp4?t=1685625982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>武器套包括4把武器，都会成为任何战士可靠的陪伴。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enfield L85A2 Custom &quot;Frankenstein&quot;</h2>Enfield L85A2 Custom。定制版英式无托型突击步枪。配置有更好的内外部组件。因此，该步枪被认为可靠、十分精准并且易于操作。容量是30子弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/ff33bba57c5001434f92a010db0b53fb.avif?t=1685625982\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DP-12 &quot;Frankenstein&quot;</h2>武器的的双枪管泵使其与你所见过的其他霰弹枪都截然不同。这款独一无二的霰弹枪不仅拥有双弹匣管，更有能造成双倍伤害的双枪管。使用这把武器的时候任何任务都是简单的很。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/986ccdfa0e33b887b73276159692a7bd.avif?t=1685625982\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SIG MPX SBR Custom &quot;Frankenstein&quot;</h2>SIG MPX SBR Custom 是一款冲锋枪，采用非常规设计，实现无与伦比的性能。它将使用者的安全性提升到了一个新的水平，并具有很高的战场适应性以及在最残酷的环境下久经考验的可靠性，开创了一个全新的冲锋枪类别。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/160082912389f1cee375b09bd4f05395.avif?t=1685625982\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AX308 &quot;Frankenstein&quot;</h2>武器采用大口径、重型穿甲子弹，可对四肢造成额外伤害。AX308 步枪是新一代系列中的第一款武器。它结合了其前代的所有优点——可靠性、耐久性、高精准度，并且由于采用了最新作战技术，还非常便于维护。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/9d1c5292f28f3f9fc7ed75f986c658f0.avif?t=1685625982\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>当然，玩家可以通过使用这些武器来争取多样的成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753580/extras/51644815748ec46f1e7a1ecc59b9dff3.avif?t=1685625982\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。",
